data.description: Nestled in the serene Mardis Subdivision this spacious gem awaits those seeking the perfect blend of comfort and privacy. Boasting nearly 3000 sq ft this residence is a harmonious haven situated in a tranquil cul-de-sac. With four bedrooms and three baths this home has room for you! The expansive layout ensures everyone has their own space to unwind. They can dive into relaxation with the private chlorine pool perfect for refreshing dips on warm summer days. The sunroom offers a versatile space for reading, morning coffee, or quiet reflection. The kitchen features all-electric appliances, creating a modern and efficient space. The primary en-suite features a jet tub and a recently renovated shower. This home is move-in ready.The property also includes a giant shop, providing a versatile space for hobbies, projects, or additional storage.Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.Call today to schedule a private tour. Your dream home awaits!
